            </h3>
            <dl class="space-y-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <dt class="text-gray-400 mb-1">Full Name</dt>
                <dd class="text-white font-medium">Agentic as a Service</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-gray-400 mb-1">Core Concept</dt>
                <dd class="text-white font-medium">Autonomous AI agents delivered as managed services</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-gray-400 mb-1">Pricing Model</dt>
                <dd class="text-white font-medium">Cost-per-Outcome (CPO)</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="text-gray-400 mb-1">Key Differentiator</dt>
                <dd class="text-white font-medium">Agents work for you vs. tools you use</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>

          {# Related Resources #}
          <div class="p-6 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl" data-reveal>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 tracking-wide mb-4">Related Resources</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <a href="/agentic-as-a-service/" class="block group">
                <p class="text-zunkiree-600 group-hover:text-zunkiree-700 leading-snug mb-1">
