                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Deep dive into the Zunkiree Agentic Stack</p>
              </a>
              <hr class="border-gray-200">
              <a href="/products/" class="block group">
                <p class="text-zunkiree-600 group-hover:text-zunkiree-700 leading-snug mb-1">
                  Zunkiree Labs Products
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">AI-native platforms built on GaaS</p>
              </a>
              <hr class="border-gray-200">
              <a href="/contact/" class="block group">
                <p class="text-zunkiree-600 group-hover:text-zunkiree-700 leading-snug mb-1">
