                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Discuss GaaS for your organization</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          {# CTA Card #}
          <div class="p-6 bg-zunkiree-50 border border-zunkiree-200 rounded-xl" data-reveal>
            <h3 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">Ready to deploy agents?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
              See how Zunkiree Labs can help you move from SaaS to GaaS with enterprise-grade infrastructure.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-4 py-3 bg-zunkiree-600 text-white font-medium hover:bg-zunkiree-700 transition-colors rounded-lg">
